; Coverage test for post.cc
; Test that the note field returns transaction note, posting note, or both.
; Tests get_note function paths:
; - post with note and xact with note (concatenated with newline)
; - post without note, xact with note (xact note only)
; - neither post nor xact have notes (NULL_VALUE)

2024/01/01 Groceries  ; xact note
    Expenses:Food    $10.00  ; post note
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 No notes
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(note)|\n'
 post note
 xact note|
 xact note|
|
|
end test
